# Files that get copied to the Proxmox node / LXC must stay LF — bash and
# Caddy choke on CRLF. This repo checkout has core.autocrlf=true and no root
# .gitattributes, so without this pin a fresh Windows checkout would rewrite
# these files to CRLF. (Added by adversarial review, 2026-07-11.)
*.sh text eol=lf
Caddyfile text eol=lf
